cc:Work.dc:title: Example 1 (with markers)
cc:Work.dc:description: A screenshot-like diagram of a file "Test.png" in a Windows 10 Desktop, which is partially selected by a selection rectangle. The file's square icon has two halves, one white and one black. The selection rectangle partially highlights the white and black rectangles. A diagram on the right side explains the Color Mixing processes, with red arrows indicating the colors involved.
